{"version":1,"content":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20260420/s00001/a4c9b5e2d26f384c23a98c1022035fa4.png\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;margin-bottom:1em\">國際嬰幼兒食品生產商HiPP「喜寶」於歐洲出售的產品懷疑被老鼠藥污染。喜寶香港指，香港並無售賣此產品，香港全線產品安全且不受事件影響。","scraped_at":"2026-04-21T01:42:08.271356+00:00","quality":{"score":0,"chars":67,"images":1,"source":"明報 本地","fallback":"rss-empty"}}